Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, February 1 (XINHUA) -- Officials with the 
Beijing Municipal Government and the Beijing Youth Federation 
held a reception this afternoon together with more than 100 
religious leaders and young clergymen. 
  Religious groups in Beijing have made contributions to the 
capital's economic development and social stability, government 
officials said. 
