<F P=100> Southwest Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Guizhou Secretary Views Family Planning Work </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK0302095894 Guiyang Guizhou People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 29 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK0302095894 </F>
<F P=104>  Guiyang Guizhou People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yesterday, provincial party committee Secretary Liu 
Fangren spoke at a family planning forum emphatically calling 
for strengthening leadership, carrying out family planning in a 
down-to-earth manner, and comprehensively improving the 
province's family planning quality. The family planning forum 
was held under the auspices of the provincial party committee 
and government and attended by prefectural, autonomous 
prefectural, and city leaders as well as comrades from the 
provincial family planning office . 
  At the forum, provincial Governor Chen Shineng relayed the 
spirit of General Secretary Jiang Zemin's instructions on family 
planning work. Zhang Yuqin, provincial vice governor and family 
planning commission director, gave an account of the province's 
family planning work and made family planning arrangements for 
1994. 
  In his speech, provincial party committee Secretary Liu 
Fangren stated: Comrade Jiang Zemin has warned us against being 
overly optimistic about family planning achievements and urged 
us to fully understand the arduousness and protractedness of 
family planning work, speak the truth,; and stop covering up 
facts and deceiving oneself and others in this regard. 
  Liu Fangren noted: Comrade Jiang Zemin's instructions fully 
tally with the realities in Guizhou. We should strive to seek 
truth from facts, boost morale, and conduct family planning in a 
down-to-earth manner. Party and government organs at all levels 
in Guizhou should implement to the letter Comrade Jiang Zemin's 
instructions on family planning work, strengthen leadership over 
family planning work, urge all departments concerned to support 
family planning work, and make more contributions to Guizhou's 
family planning work. 
  Also attending the forum were Long Zhiyi, Wang Siqi, Li 
Wanlu, Liu Yulin, Miao Chunting, and some other leading comrades. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-26168 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drchi023_s_94001" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-CHI-94-023 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  3 Feb 1994 </DATE1>

