<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] On the morning of 3 February, Jinan's Nanjiao 
Guest House was filled with thoughts of love and an enthusiastic 
atmosphere as the Shandong Provincial CPC Committee and the 
provincial people's government jointly sponsored the Spring 
Festival tea party for personages from various social circles. 
Participants gathered together happily for 1994's Spring 
Festival. 
  Jiang Chunyun, secretary of the provincial party committee, 
