across the province; various mass organizations; nonparty 
patriotic personages; representative personages of national and 
religious circles; nonparty intellectuals; representative 
personages from non-publicly-owned enterprises; compatriots from 
Taiwan, Hong Kong, and Macao and overseas Chinese, who are 
currently in the province; as well as friends of various 
circles, who have shown concern and support, and provided help 
in the province's program of modernization. [passage omitted] 
