<H3> <TI>   Henan Telecommunication Volume Grows </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK0302130994 Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 29 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK0302130994 </F>
<F P=104>  Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] In 1993, Henan's total telecommunication volume 
registered a 72.8 percent over 1992 with its total number of 
telephone exchangers reaching 0.77 million. 
  Except for Quxian, Huaibin, and Shangcheng counties, all 
cities and counties in the province installed national 
direct-dial long-distance telephones. Seventeen prefectures and 
cities and some counties in the province installed international 
direct-dial long-distance telephones. 
  Last year, the province also succeeded in rapidly developing 
various paging services with the result that 17 prefectures and 
cities and 35 counties and districts in the province installed 
900 mobile paging antennas. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

