Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] The autonomous regional party committee and the 
regional people's government jointly sponsored a tea party for 
the Spring Festival in the region's Xincheng Guest House for 
veteran cadres of regional level organs on the afternoon of 2 
February. 
